  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the safety and efficacy of an ocular sirolimus
      (rapamycin) formulation compared to Placebo on the signs and symptoms of dry eye in the CAE
      Model.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
